texconfig supports adjusting and updating many aspects of
the TeX installation.

Usage: texconfig conf                  (show configuration information)
       texconfig dvipdfmx paper PAPER  (dvipdfmx paper size)
       texconfig dvips [OPTION...]     (dvips options)
       texconfig faq                   (show pointer to TeX Live docs)
       texconfig findprog PROG...      (show locations of PROGs, a la which)
       texconfig font vardir DIR
       texconfig font ro
       texconfig font rw
       texconfig formats               (edit fmtutil.cnf)
       texconfig help                  (or --help; show this help)
       texconfig hyphen FORMAT         (edit hyphenation config for FORMAT)
       texconfig init [FORMAT]...      (rebuild FORMATs, or all formats
                                        plus run texlinks and updmap)
       texconfig mode MODE             (set Metafont MODE)
       texconfig paper PAPER           (set default paper size to PAPER)
       texconfig pdftex [OPTION]...    (pdftex options)
       texconfig rehash                (rebuild ls-R files with mktexlsr)
       texconfig version               (or --version; show version info)
       texconfig xdvi paper PAPER      (xdvi paper size)

Get more help with:
       texconfig dvipdfmx
       texconfig dvips
       texconfig font
       texconfig hyphen
       texconfig mode
       texconfig paper
       texconfig pdftex
       texconfig xdvi

Report bugs to: tex-k@tug.org
TeX Live home page: <http://tug.org/texlive/>

